description: Try our easy to follow 4-Step Chicken Parmigiana recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: 4-Step Chicken Parmigiana Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 500g sweet potato, peeled, cut into long wedges
400g can diced tomatoes with onion, garlic and basil

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 220Â°C. Line a baking tray with baking paper. Spread sweet potato on tray and spray with oil. Place on top shelf of oven and bake for 25 minutes or until tender and golden.
Place chicken in a shallow baking dish and spoon over tomatoes.
Combine breadcrumbs and parmesan in a bowl. Sprinkle mixture over chicken and bake for 15-20 minutes or until chicken is cooked through and topping is golden and crisp.
Meanwhile, bring a saucepan of water to the boil. Add beans and cook for 2 minutes or until just tender. Drain. Serve chicken with sweet potato and beans.
